CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 17, reads: "...9. The Metropolitan Pepsi-Cola Bottling Company booth had Miss Kittie Curtis of Duquesne University and Bill J. Brown, sales supervisor, serving cold Pepsis to thirsty visitors..."
TitMainTitle: Kittie Curtis and Bill J. Brown serving Pepsi in Pepsi-Cola booth for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Syria Mosque
